<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Relatório Trimestral - Ouvidoria da ANTAQ</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png"
    href="https://prd-apex.antaq.gov.br/ords/r/sfc/120/files/static/v119/icons/app-icon-32.png" />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free@6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: url('img_porto.jpeg') center center / cover no-repeat;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10, 34, 54, 0.72) 0%, rgba(16, 48, 80, 0.55) 50%, rgba(22, 70, 110, 0.45) 100%);
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .header-bar {
      background-color: #103050;
      height: 12px;
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .secondary-bar {
      background-color: #0070C0;
      height: 6px;
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .font-montserrat {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }

    .org-bar {
      padding: 20px 40px 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .org-bar .org-title {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .org-bar .org-sub {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #E2E8F0;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .main {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 24px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .header-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .header-section .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #0090C0;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .header-section .eyebrow::before,
    .header-section .eyebrow::after {
      content: "";
      width: 34px;
      height: 2px;
      background: #0090C0;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .header-section h1 {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 4.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    }

    .header-section h1 .gold {
      color: #0090C0;
    }

    .header-section p {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      font-weight: 900;
      padding: 8px 18px;
      background-color: rgba(16, 48, 80, 0.55);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
      text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .cards {
      display: flex;
      gap: 28px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      max-width: 1300px;
    }

    .card {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.58);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
      border-left: 6px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      border-radius: 16px;
      width: 380px;
      padding: 32px 28px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: transform .3s cubic-bezier(.2, .7, .3, 1), background-color .3s ease, box-shadow .3s ease, border-color .3s ease;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      animation: cardIn .55s cubic-bezier(.2, .7, .3, 1) both;
    }

    .cards .card:nth-child(2) {
      animation-delay: .1s;
    }

    .cards .card:nth-child(3) {
      animation-delay: .2s;
    }

    @keyframes cardIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(22px);
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: none;
      }
    }

    .card-relatorio {
      border-left-color: #0070C0;
    }

    .card-falabr {
      border-left-color: #103050;
    }

    .card-portal {
      border-left-color: #0090C0;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(16, 48, 80, 0.28);
    }

    .card-relatorio:hover {
      border-color: #0070C0;
    }

    .card-portal:hover {
      border-color: #0090C0;
    }

    .card-icon {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: transform .3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover .card-icon {
      transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-6deg);
    }

    .card-relatorio .card-icon {
      background-color: #DBEAFE;
      color: #0070C0;
    }

    .card-falabr .card-icon {
      background-color: #E0E7FF;
      color: #103050;
    }

    .card-portal .card-icon {
      background-color: #E1F2F8;
      color: #0090C0;
    }

    .card-content h2 {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1E293B;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .card-content p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #1E293B;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .card-link {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      transition: gap 0.2s ease;
    }

    .card-relatorio .card-link {
      color: #0070C0;
    }

    .card-falabr .card-link {
      color: #103050;
    }

    .card-portal .card-link {
      color: #0090C0;
    }

    .card:hover .card-link {
      gap: 11px;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 18px 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
      background-color: rgba(16, 48, 80, 0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      color: #FFFFFF;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .footer-channels {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .footer-channels .channels-title {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: #CBD5E1;
    }

    .footer-channels .channels-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .footer-channels .channels-links a {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #BBD2E8;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color .2s ease;
    }

    .footer-channels .channels-links a:hover {
      color: #FFFFFF;
    }

    .footer-credit {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .footer-credit .anchor-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: #0090C0;
      color: #103050;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .footer-credit p {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #CBD5E1;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {

      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        animation: none !important;
        transition: none !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="header-bar"></div>
  <div class="secondary-bar"></div>

  <div class="org-bar">
    <img src="sistema/Imagens/Logo Horizontal_Branca_C_N.png" alt="Logo ANTAQ" style="height: 78px; width: auto;" />
  </div>

  <div class="main">
    <div class="header-section">
      <h1>Ouvidoria <span class="gold">da ANTAQ</span></h1>
      <p>Selecione o conteúdo que deseja acessar</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards">
      <a class="card card-relatorio" href="#"
        onclick="event.preventDefault(); window.open('sistema/index.html', '_blank');">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-column"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <h2>Relatório Trimestral 2026</h2>
          <p>Dados consolidados das manifestações do 1º trimestre (Jan–Mar).</p>
          <span class="card-link">Abrir apresentação <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-channels">
      <span class="channels-title">Canais oficiais ANTAQ</span>
      <div class="channels-links">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ANTAQ.oficial" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i><span>Facebook</span></a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/antaq_oficial/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i><span>Instagram</span></a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/c/CanalANTAQ/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i><span>YouTube</span></a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/antaq" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i><span>LinkedIn</span></a>
        <a href="https://x.com/ANTAQ_oficial" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i><span>Twitter</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-credit">
      <div class="anchor-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-anchor"></i></div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>

</html>